response.overview: The 2023 World Series film presents the story of the 1st World Series championship in Texas Rangers franchise history. Manager Bruce Bochy led the Rangers to an unprecedented 11-0 Postseason road record, defeating the Arizona Diamondbacks four games to one behind the historically productive bats of Corey Seager and Adolis Garcia and shutout pitching in the Fall Classic clincher by Nathan Eovaldi.
response.title: 2023 World Series Champions: Texas Rangers
